-- Russia’s Usmanov Buys New $100 Million Yacht, Izvestia Says
-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 2012-06-01T05:00:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-01/russia-s-usmanov-buys-new-100-million-yacht-izvestia-says.html
Billionaire  Alisher Usmanov ,  Russia ’s
richest man and an investor in  Facebook Inc. (FB) , bought a new $100
million yacht,  Izvestia  reported today, without saying where it
obtained the information.  Usmanov sold his previous 66 meter-long yacht and gave the
new one the same name - Dilbar, the name of his mother, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yuliya Fedorinova in Moscow at 
 yfedorinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
